phrases: Crap, that is the second bell.
We are not going to make it!
Whose fault is it this time?!
And now we are all late!
You are all in the same class, so get Rin in there first to get yourselves excused!
Throw her to the third floor!
It will be easy enough if Kengo and Masato work together!
Should not be a problem with Rin's reflexes.
Why do I have to work with this loser?
This is too dangerous for you.
But seriously, Rin must have hit a record altitude!
What is that about awesome, Retard?!
I will throw gentler next time...
There will not be a next time!
You can call me Muscles-san, too.
They are helping the Disciplinary Committee with their patrols.
He sent them here from Finland so I would not be lonely.
Coincidentally, I am a girl too.
So I am Strelka and Belka's big sister!
I have been taking care of them since they were this little.
They were naughty little rascals back then.
They are dogs, but they are even smarter than me now.
The fact that you admit that is, uh...
We could use her on our team!
You transferred here recently after moving back to Japan, right?
We would like you to join us.
Do you want to play baseball with us?
We need more people on our team.
They do not care for baseball in the country that Noumi-kun lived in.
It is something like baseball in English.
The name of our team is Little Busters.
It will be a lot of fun if you join!
And you will get some muscles on you if you play, too.
I do not know anything about baseball.
I do not know anything about it either.
I have no clue what I am doing!
These two make a good case for it.
Either way, how about giving it a try, Noumi?
So I catch the ball with this?
Just catch it like you did with the frisbee earlier.
Should we try with her a bit farther away, Kyousuke?
A bit farther back and to my right!
Did my Roger just now sound native?
Man, she is like a little dog...
It seems we have found a diamond in the rough.
Starting today, Noumi Kudryavka is a member of the Little Busters.
My first friends since coming to this school...
I do not know what to say...
I hope we can be the best of friends!
I am very happy to have another cute girl on our team.
I am going to spin you all day long!
Oh, it is the Resident Assistant!
It must be another package from Grandpa.
She is not fine at all.
Let us help you with that, Kud-o.
No, um, that is what we are supposed to say.
That makes us sound like dangerous people.
You are taking these to your room, right?
Boys cannot come into the girls' dorm.
I heard recently that the Disciplinary Committee posts guards around it...
He sends a lot of things to help me blend in with Japanese culture.
Are you staying alone in this room?
I do not have a roommate.
You can call us musclemates, too.
No idea what musclemates are, but we are roommates.
We submitted a request, and they granted it.
We have known each other since we were kids, so the RA probably took that into consideration.
Being good friends is a very good thing.
When I was little, I moved from country to country, so I have never known anyone for that long.
And... I have a hard time making friends.
Do you want a roommate, Kud?
I hope I can find one.
I do not like being alone.
Sounds like you get lonely easily.
So basically, you need someone in your room to be on muscles duty.
He might not look it, but he is got some good muscles under those clothes.
He will be an amazing muscles dutyman in the future.
You would not feel lonely with Riki here, right?
But would not that mean I would be alone?
Then it would be like you did not like me anymore!
Do not cry just from imagining it...
My heart is as naive as toilet paper.
Maybe you should train that instead of your muscles.
Roommates are as wonderful as I thought!
Why do not you ask the RA about it, Kud?
I will sign off on the search and the move.
But the new term just started.
It will be hard finding someone who wants to change rooms.
Anyway, I will put a memo on the billboard for you about looking for a roommate.
I will send something out on the mailing list about it too.
But if no one responds, we will end the search there.
I hope you can find someone.
We will be together for a long time.
But now that that is over, you boys had better go back to your dorm.
If the Disciplinary Committee finds you, they will kill you.
It seems it is always you people causing trouble.
But this is quite a blatant infraction right here.
Naoe-san and Inohara-san came here to help me
Regardless of the reason, boys are not allowed in the girls' dorm.
All three of you will be writing formal apologies.
Damn it, it is like her blood are not red!
Futaki Kanata, the Ice Queen of the Disciplinary Committee?
Her and the counselor held us for an hour after that to wring us out,
I am very sorry about that.
Your tiny body'll get tinier if you are down.
We are waiting on approval from the student council's executive committee for that.
We are cracking down extra hard on rule-breakers this month.
More importantly, about Noumi's search for a roommate
I saw your ad in the mailing list!
I am in a triple, so I am full up!
I would spin you around three times a day if we were roommates!
Komari, do not you have a roommate too?
You do not have a roommate, right?
When is she going to get over her shyness?
We have another girl without a roommate!
It looks like she is skipping class today too.
You want to be my roommate, Kudryavka-kun?
We heard that there were a lot of people who wanted to be your roommate,
but you turned them all down.
Being alone is easier for me.
But Kud should not bother you.
Oh, do you feel lonely, little girl?
It seems I have gone too far.
Ah, hugging Kudryavka-kun at a 45-degree angle feels best.
Are you okay with that, Little Miss Noumi?
Are you trying to kill me painfully, boy?
Being roommates means that she would be sleeping right next to me at night.
What am I supposed to do?
Just imagine her sitting on her bed in her pajamas after a shower.
I would get on top of her without a second thought.
She is too dangerous to be Kud's roommate!
Sorry, let us ask someone else.
I guess I would just bother Kurugaya-san if we were roommates.
Kurugaya-san is so well-proportioned, tall, smart, good at English,
has such big breasts, and acts so grown-up.
Meanwhile, I am poorly proportioned, short, stupid, bad at English,
do not have any breasts, and act like such a kid.
Now I feel really sad after saying that.
You do not know her yet?
Well, I guess she does not have much of a presence.
I have never seen her talk with anyone.
She might not have a roommate either.
Why do not you try asking her?
It is kind of hard to approach her.
If you do not mind us asking, do you have a roommate?
I am looking for a roommate.
I have a lot of things.
I read anything, so it is a chaotic mix,
but I recently finished a book on Fermat's Last Theorem.
But maybe it was not interesting.
Which direction does your room face?
My books fell, all at once.
You would not have been able to escape.
You would have been stranded in the dorm.
That is a lot of books...
I think I would just be a bother after all.
I am sorry, but I must respectfully decline.
So you could not find a roommate for Noumi.
Today's the deadline for it too...
The RA came by to tell me a minute ago.
Apparently, no one asked about being my roommate.
It might be nice being alone!
I am already unbelievably happy to be part of the Little Busters.
A roommate would be asking for too much.
It might be better this way.
So no one volunteered to be Kud's roommate?
She is a funny little foreigner, after all.
You are not allowed to take that magazine from the library.
It seems you have not found a roommate yet.
I will put a request in to the RA later today.
I do not have a roommate either.
My room is too big, so there is some space.
You can move into my room.
It is not like you have anyone else.
Strelka, Belka, we are going on our evening patrol.
Why the head of the Disciplinary Committee of all people?
Kud, if you do not want her, you can turn her down.
Thanks to all of you, I have finally found a roommate!
None of the lunch ladies are here today!
Let us cover the kitchen for them!
It is time for Muscles-chan here!
